      "title": "问题解决：Ubuntu 下 IDEA 复制中文变问号乱码",
      "url": "https://xmkdgdz.github.io/2026/04/23/%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%EF%BC%9AUbuntu-%E4%B8%8B-IDEA-%E5%A4%8D%E5%88%B6%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87%E5%8F%98%E9%97%AE%E5%8F%B7%E4%B9%B1%E7%A0%81/",
