      "text": "<p 最近在写一个Java项目，需要操作到 ClickHouse 数据库，手写 SQL 完成各种操作。在这中间遇到不少 bug，此处记录一下解决方法。</p <h2 id=\"批量插入操作\" <a href=\"#批量插入操作\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"批量插入操作\" </a 批量插入操作</h2 <h3 id=\"问题描述\" <a href=\"#问题描述\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"问题描述\" </a 问题描述</h3 <p 在批量插入操作中，出现如下报错：</p <blockquote <p 信息经脱敏处理</p </blockquote <figure class=\"highlight yaml\" <table <tr <td class=\"gutter\" <pre <span class=\"line\" 1</span <br <span class=\"line\" 2</span <br <span class=\"line\" 3</span <br <span class=\"line\" 4</span <br <span class=\"line\" 5</span <br <span class=\"line\" 6</span <br <span class=\"line\" 7</span <br <span class=\"line\" 8</span <br <span class=\"line\" 9</span <br </pre </td <td class=\"code\" <pre <code class=\"hljs YAML\" <span class=\"hljs attr\" ru.yandex.clickhouse.except.ClickHouseException:</span <span class=\"hljs string\" ClickHouse</span <span class=\"hljs string\" exception,</span <span class=\"hljs attr\" code:</span <span class=\"hljs number\" 27</span <span class=\"hljs string\" ,</span <span class=\"hljs attr\" host:</span [<span class=\"hljs string\" HOST IP</span ]<span class=\"hljs string\" ,</span <span class=\"hljs attr\" port:</span <span class=\"hljs number\" 8123</span <span class=\"hljs string\" ;</span <span class=\"hljs attr\" Code:</span <span class=\"hljs number\" 27</span <span class=\"hljs string\" ,</span <span class=\"hljs string\" e.displayText()</span <span class=\"hljs string\" =</span <span class=\"hljs attr\" DB::ParsingException: Cannot parse input:</span <span class=\"hljs string\" expected</span <span clas"
